# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy the secret values into a file named `.env.local` (which is
# git-ignored via `*.local`) so they are NEVER committed/pushed.
# The public Supabase values live in `.env` and are safe to commit.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Server-side only. Powers the AI concierge (/api/concierge).
# Get one at https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# ⚠️ Put the REAL key in `.env.local` (git-ignored), NOT here.
OPENAI_API_KEY=

# Optional. Defaults to gpt-4.1-mini (best value for this concierge:
# strong instruction-following + grounding, fast, cheap).
# Cheaper: gpt-4o-mini. Newer: gpt-5-mini / gpt-5-nano.
OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4.1-mini
